<header>
	
		
		The beginning of Part 1 of the IELTS Speaking Module is easy, in that you can prepare for it. The questions ask for specific details about you. The Examiner will say "Good morning", or "Good afternoon", or "Good evening". You should respond in the same way.
</header>
	
